      "rationale": "All 13 model inputs (fluid properties, boundary conditions, geometric parameters, hemolysis model coefficients) are documented with nominal values and sources. Input uncertainty distributions were specified for Monte Carlo UQ: fluid viscosity (CV 3%), rotational speed (CV 1%), inlet flow rate (CV 2%), and power-law exponents (literature range). Achieved level meets required level. Note: the Monte Carlo UQ propagates these distributions comprehensively across the full input space, confirming RH < 1.0 at the 95th percentile."
