    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors are appropriately scoped as not-assessed per MRL 2 requirements. Uncertainty quantification via comprehensive Monte Carlo analysis across all model inputs confirms that the relative hemolysis index remains below the RH < 1.0 acceptance criterion at the 95th percentile across all five operating points. The model is accepted as credible for the stated COU of identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device.",
